		bodyMsg.append("<li>  Trainings, videos, explanation on <b>tools</b> used on HERMES - <a href:https://e-3d-jira.capgemini.com/confluence/display/HERK/Tools>https://e-3d-jira.capgemini.com/confluence/display/HERK/Tools</a></li></ul></b><br/>");
		
		bodyMsg.append("NB2: Use the search field on the top right hand side of the page to search for any specific topic<br/>");
